Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 村主 身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那暂时不给你排班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体健康最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想办法整合下现有人员的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪异…怪异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不…全勤奖的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 兼职是没有全勤奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
